Description: Install udev rules in the correct location
Author: Jakob Ketterl <jakob.ketterl@gmx.de>

* udev files should not go into bindir. This patch sets the correct path.
* also gets rid of hooks to create linux groups, this is done by postinst.
--- a/Makefile.am
+++ b/Makefile.am
